when FontFreeType::getGlyphBitmap return a zero-size char array.
to reproduce:
```
auto pLabel = Label::create("{1} + {2}", "TTF/xxxx.TTF", 24);
pLabel->enableOutline(Color4B(0xFF, 0xFF, 0xFF, 255), 1);
addChild(pLabel);
```

